# WhatsApp notifications (optional). Uses CallMeBot — free, no Twilio.
# Get your key: https://www.callmebot.com/blog/free-api-whatsapp-messages/
# 1. Add +34 644 66 32 62 to contacts, send "I allow callmebot to send me messages"
# 2. You receive an API key; set it and your phone (E.164, e.g. +15551234567) below.
# If unset, recordings still save; you just won't get a WhatsApp alert.

# CALLMEBOT_WHATSAPP_APIKEY=your_api_key_here
# CALLMEBOT_WHATSAPP_PHONE=+15551234567
